    "display_name": "Karma",
    "long_instructions": "### Karma\r\n\r\nRecreate the chorus for Karma by Denzel Kennedy. There are 4 different vocal lyrics - use all 4 in any order you want!\r\n\r\nHere are some tips for re-creating this code:\r\n- Make sure all your vocals are in the `play sequential` block [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:play_toolbox---id-up-inside:play_sequential_workspace)\r\n- You'll need three `repeat` blocks - one for the beats, one for the bass, one for the lead. [<i class=\"fa-solid fa-lightbulb\"></i> <i class=\"fa-solid fa-square-right\"></i>](#clickable=flyout-id:repeat_toolbox---id:play_sequential_workspace)\r\n\r\nYour final song should look like the example below\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/f912b3c60bc7476b6be0a66c84221761-image-1744323448206.png)",
    "bubble_choice_description": "Recreate the chorus to Karma by Denzel Kennedy",
